lead_paragraph: Pablo Carreno Busta of Spain ousted top-seeded Gilles Simon 6-3, 6-4 in the Estoril Open quarterfinals on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Carreno Busta Beats Top-Seeded Simon to Reach Estoril Semis
